{
  "_comment_general": "Dashboard de CloudWatch para el módulo notas-venta del Examen 2 (expediente 750843). Para importarlo: AWS Console → CloudWatch → Dashboards → Create dashboard → 'View/edit source' (icono </>) → pegar este JSON. El dashboard contiene los 2 widgets que pide el enunciado: percentiles p50/p90/p99 del tiempo de ejecución, y comportamiento (counts por familia 2xx/4xx/5xx).",
  "widgets": [
    {
      "_comment": "Widget 1 — Percentiles p50/p90/p99 de duración del POST /sales. Cumple requisito 9.i del enunciado. Calculados por CloudWatch a partir del histograma de samples de HttpRequestDurationMs.",
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "metrics": [
          [
            "Examen2/750843",
            "HttpRequestDurationMs",
            "Environment",
            "production",
            "Route",
            "POST /sales",
            "StatusFamily",
            "2xx",
            { "stat": "p50", "label": "p50" }
          ],
          [
            "...",
            { "stat": "p90", "label": "p90" }
          ],
          [
            "...",
            { "stat": "p99", "label": "p99" }
          ]
        ],
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": false,
        "region": "us-east-1",
        "period": 60,
        "title": "Latencia POST /sales (p50, p90, p99) — production",
        "yAxis": {
          "left": {
            "label": "Milisegundos",
            "showUnits": false
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Widget 2 — Comportamiento HTTP del módulo, contando requests por familia de status. Cumple requisito 9.ii del enunciado. Permite ver de un vistazo si el servicio está sano (mayoría 2xx) o con problemas (picos en 4xx/5xx).",
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "metrics": [
          [
            "Examen2/750843",
            "HttpRequestCount",
            "Environment",
            "production",
            "Route",
            "POST /sales",
            "StatusFamily",
            "2xx",
            { "stat": "Sum", "label": "2xx OK" }
          ],
          [
            "...",
            "StatusFamily",
            "4xx",
            { "stat": "Sum", "label": "4xx Client Error" }
          ],
          [
            "...",
            "StatusFamily",
            "5xx",
            { "stat": "Sum", "label": "5xx Server Error" }
          ]
        ],
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": true,
        "region": "us-east-1",
        "period": 60,
        "title": "Comportamiento HTTP POST /sales (2xx vs 4xx vs 5xx) — production",
        "yAxis": {
          "left": {
            "label": "Requests por minuto",
            "showUnits": false
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Widget extra 1 — Vista general del servicio con todas las rutas instrumentadas. Sirve para detectar de un golpe qué endpoint está fallando.",
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 6,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "metrics": [
          [
            { "expression": "SEARCH('Namespace=\"Examen2/750843\" MetricName=\"HttpRequestCount\" Environment=\"production\" StatusFamily=\"5xx\"', 'Sum', 60)", "label": "5xx por ruta", "id": "e1" }
          ]
        ],
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": false,
        "region": "us-east-1",
        "period": 60,
        "title": "Errores 5xx por ruta — production"
      }
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Widget extra 2 — Comparativa local vs production con la misma métrica. Confirma que la dimensión Environment está discriminando ambientes (requisito 7.iii).",
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 6,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "metrics": [
          [
            "Examen2/750843",
            "HttpRequestCount",
            "Environment",
            "local",
            "Route",
            "POST /sales",
            "StatusFamily",
            "2xx",
            { "stat": "Sum", "label": "local 2xx" }
          ],
          [
            "...",
            "Environment",
            "production",
            ".",
            ".",
            ".",
            ".",
            { "stat": "Sum", "label": "production 2xx" }
          ]
        ],
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": false,
        "region": "us-east-1",
        "period": 60,
        "title": "POST /sales 2xx — local vs production"
      }
    }
  ]
}
